{"url": "https://www.dofus.com/en/mmorpg/encyclopedia/consumables/13314-magic-portable-balloon", "id": 13314, "name": "Magic Portable Balloon", "img": "http://staticns.ankama.com/dofus/www/game/items/200/94014.png", "type": "Various", "level": 1, "description": "Contrary to the fake ones that one might find at the Trool Fair, this balloon won't deflate and will follow you no matter the danger. It was made by hand out of pet shadows and good old-fashioned Astrubian fish glue, using the traditional recipe by Berry Pills."}